replies.msg:
Torreira on why he chose Arsenal: &ldquo;It was the best option. This is a huge club with massive support across the world. The fans &amp; everyone associated with the club have made me feel so welcome. I really feel like a part of the family here.&rdquo; [FourFourTwo] #afc<br />
<br />
Lucas Torreira: &ldquo;It&rsquo;s been a pretty big change for me. Genoa is a much smaller city than London, but every week I feel more comfortable &amp; learn new things about the way of life. When I arrived, we saw traditional landmarks, trying to get my bearings. Now it feels more like home.&rdquo;

